&lt;h1 id="ideas-are-the-new-oil"&gt;Ideas Are the New Oil&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nov 17 2021&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All the new fortunes are created with ideas&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Naval:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Humans have a history of conquest because we fight for the same exact resources, but even in human history the first explorers were traders. They were going out there to find spices, gold, silk, new plants to domesticate, new animals.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>It’s Mind Blowing That Our Minds Can’t Be Blown</title><link>https://linguage.github.io/naval/orig/its-mind-blowing-that-our-minds-cant-be-blown/</link><pubDate>Sat, 30 Oct 2021 18:42:13 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguage.github.io/naval/orig/its-mind-blowing-that-our-minds-cant-be-blown/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://linguage.github.io/naval/zh/its-mind-blowing-that-our-minds-cant-be-blown.zh/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
