&lt;h1 id="the-best-essay"&gt;The Best Essay&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;March 2024&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Despite its title this isn&amp;rsquo;t meant to be the best essay. My goal here is to figure out what the best essay would be like.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It would be well-written, but you can write well about any topic. What made it special would be what it was about.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>The Need to Read</title><link>https://linguage.github.io/paul_graham/essays_en/read/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguage.github.io/paul_graham/essays_en/read/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;→ &lt;a href="https://linguage.github.io/paul_graham/essays_zh/read/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
